text: Anthonia is a Swedish, Danish, and Finnish feminine given name that is a form of Antonia that is used in Finland, Denmark, Sweden, Republic of Karelia, Estonia and Greenland. Notable individuals with the name include: * Anthonia Adenike Adeniji (1971-), Nigerian academic * Anthonia Fatunsin, Nigerian archeologist * Anthonia Kleinhoonte (1887-1960), Dutch botanist and experimentalist ==See also== ==Notes== Category:Danish feminine given names Category:Finnish feminine given names Category:Swedish feminine given names Category:Feminine given names
title: Anthonia
